Explore the Microsoft.Agents.AI NuGet package API surface. I need to understand how to use ChatClientAgent with tools.

1. Decompile or list public types in /home/runner/.nuget/packages/microsoft.agents.ai/1.4.0/lib/net9.0/Microsoft.Agents.AI.dll using `dotnet tool` or reflection. Try:
```
cd /tmp/sv-cacb0bb9f50844da96ea6535da9f203d/ResearchAgent
dotnet run --project . 2>&1 || true
```

Actually, use ildasm or a simple C# script to list the public types and methods:
```bash
cd /tmp/sv-cacb0bb9f50844da96ea6535da9f203d/ResearchAgent

# Create a temp script to list types
cat > /tmp/list_types.csx << 'EOF'
using System.Reflection;
var asm = Assembly.LoadFrom("/home/runner/.nuget/packages/microsoft.agents.ai/1.4.0/lib/net9.0/Microsoft.Agents.AI.dll");
foreach (var t in asm.GetExportedTypes().OrderBy(t => t.FullName))
{
    Console.WriteLine($"\n=== {t.FullName} ===");
    foreach (var m in t.GetMethods(BindingFlags.Public | BindingFlags.Instance | BindingFlags.Static | BindingFlags.DeclaredOnly))
        Console.WriteLine($"  {m.ReturnType.Name} {m.Name}({string.Join(", ", m.GetParameters().Select(p => $"{p.ParameterType.Name} {p.Name}"))})");
    foreach (var p in t.GetProperties(BindingFlags.Public | BindingFlags.Instance | BindingFlags.DeclaredOnly))
        Console.WriteLine($"  prop {p.PropertyType.Name} {p.Name}");
    foreach (var c in t.GetConstructors())
        Console.WriteLine($"  ctor({string.Join(", ", c.GetParameters().Select(p => $"{p.ParameterType.Name} {p.Name}"))})");
}
EOF
```

Actually, the simplest approach is just using reflection in a temp program. Do this:

```bash
cd /tmp/sv-cacb0bb9f50844da96ea6535da9f203d

mkdir -p /tmp/type-explorer && cd /tmp/type-explorer
cat > Program.cs << 'ENDPROG'
using System.Reflection;

var agentsPath = "/home/runner/.nuget/packages/microsoft.agents.ai/1.4.0/lib/net9.0/Microsoft.Agents.AI.dll";
var meaiPath = "/home/runner/.nuget/packages/microsoft.extensions.ai/10.5.2/lib/net9.0/Microsoft.Extensions.AI.dll";
var absPath = Directory.GetFiles("/home/runner/.nuget/packages/microsoft.extensions.ai.abstractions/", "Microsoft.Extensions.AI.Abstractions.dll", SearchOption.AllDirectories).OrderDescending().First();

// Load dependencies first
Assembly.LoadFrom(absPath);
Assembly.LoadFrom(meaiPath);
var asm = Assembly.LoadFrom(agentsPath);

foreach (var t in asm.GetExportedTypes().OrderBy(t => t.FullName))
{
    Console.WriteLine($"\n=== {t.FullName} ===");
    if (t.BaseType != null && t.BaseType != typeof(object))
        Console.WriteLine($"  extends {t.BaseType.FullName}");
    foreach (var iface in t.GetInterfaces().Where(i => i.IsPublic))
        Console.WriteLine($"  implements {iface.FullName}");
    foreach (var c in t.GetConstructors(BindingFlags.Public | BindingFlags.Instance))
        Console.WriteLine($"  ctor({string.Join(", ", c.GetParameters().Select(p => $"{p.ParameterType.Name} {p.Name}"))})");
    foreach (var p in t.GetProperties(BindingFlags.Public | BindingFlags.Instance | BindingFlags.DeclaredOnly))
        Console.WriteLine($"  prop {p.PropertyType.Name} {p.Name} {{ {(p.CanRead?"get;":"")}{(p.CanWrite?" set;":"")} }}");
    foreach (var m in t.GetMethods(BindingFlags.Public | BindingFlags.Instance | BindingFlags.Static | BindingFlags.DeclaredOnly).Where(m => !m.IsSpecialName))
        Console.WriteLine($"  {(m.IsStatic?"static ":"")}{m.ReturnType.Name} {m.Name}({string.Join(", ", m.GetParameters().Select(p => $"{p.ParameterType.Name} {p.Name}"))})");
